<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - الصَّمْتُ غُنْمٌ لأَقْوَامٍ وَمَسْتَرةٌ ... وَالْقَوْلُ فِي بَعْضِهِ التَّضْلِيلُ وَالْفَنَدُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٤٦)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ صَالِحُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْقُدُّوسِ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الكامل)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - لا تُكْثِرَنْ حَشْوَ الْكَلا ... مِ إِذَا اهْتَدَيْتَ إِلَى عُيُونِهْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - وَالصَّمْتُ أَحْسَنُ بِالْفَتَى ... مِنْ مَنْطقٍ فِي غَيْر حِينِهْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٤٧)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيضْاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الرمل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - أطِلِ الصَّمْتَ فَإِنَّ الصَّمْتَ حُكْمٌ ... وَإِذَا قُمْتَ فَبِالْحَقِّ فَقُمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٤٨)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - وَلَلصَّمْتُ خَيْرٌ منْ كَلامٍ بِمَأْثَمٍ ... فَكُنْ صَامِتاً تَسْلَمْ وَإِنْ قُلْتَ فَاعْدِلِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
